    <div xml:id="PN246-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai – atu. tuṟai – āṉantappaiyuḷ. 
      pūtapāṇṭiyaṉṟēvi peruṅkōpeṇṭu tīppāyvāḷ colliyatu. 
ituvumatu – <app>
<lem wit="#C8">pūtappāṇṭiyaṉ</lem>
<rdg wit="#C2 #C3"><gap quantity="17" unit="character"/>ṭiṉa</rdg>
</app> 
<app>
